Installation
=============================

This application requires the pre-installation of the cmake tool,
a C++ compiler and comes with pre-installed libraries.

In case clear-all is used to remove libraries and executables
you can install libraries libdivsufsort and sdsl on Linux via

$ ./pre-install.sh 

The shell command `make -f Makefile' should compile this program. 

Instructions
==================

This installation includes the pre-installation of WPT code and the 
libraries: libdivsufsort and sdsl.

The shell command `make -f Makefile' should compile this program. 
   
After compilation the binary `run' will be created in the working 
directory. You may call it from this directory via

$  ./run -l ./data/left.fastq -r ./data/right.fastq -o output.txt
